column5: Very Cool reel Geoff
Enjoy the reel, Geoff.
Nice one Geoff! Did the guy at Rona tell you that you need two of those? One at each end of the yard?  I'm just envious is all.
I didn't recognized it was you, but than we never met before....
Oh dang, nice to meet you too Jackie!  Thanks for the deal as I like it and I hope to try and test it out again this weekend.
I had a very hard time turning down a brand new Okuma Raw-II for $xxx so I got one.  Looks like I'm heading back to the rivers again...
Nice reel Geoff,they have dropped that much?,or just a good deal. I know a fellow that has some pretty good luck with one of those. Enjoy!
Ok, spill the beans brother. Where did ya steal that from?  Good reel for the price.
No, I made my own Sail, um er sale....    Someone at any other store must be selling it for less....
my hand turns into a cramped claw just looking at it
must be that pinky thing you do...
:rofl2:  :rofl2:   I wonder if Extream will match the price? Like to support.
that was the only finger that wasn't cramped and I was still able to straiten it without help
The horror!  I start on the river soon, see you out there.
Will you be match pricing Phil? I would be interested in another in the next couple of weeks.
yeah man, I'll be out between the kids hockey games...
For OFC'ers, always if I can!
Sweet toy Geoff. I'm sure you'll have a blast breaking it in
Thanks Mike. I can't wait to 'pop' it!

NO NO SAY IT ANIT SO ...GBW HAS GONE OVER TO THE DARK SIDE >>> DUDE I live on my boat ,its in the water year round ,get clean of this sin and we can go to the blue water all winter , between the nuke outfall and 400 hundred feet, so so many fish to catch NO NEED TO RUB SHOULDERS WITH "The Masses" >>> AHHHHHHHHH , You and Bill, dude NO say it isnt so , not that there is anything wrong with that , but the thought of you two fighting to carry solos gear ... bad bad , ... lmao ... Sinclare Im comeing with ya
^---- LOL!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!   Bruce, you crack me up man   :clapping:
LMAO @ Capt!  I'll gladly join ya any day we can make it happen!!!
You wont regret it.

GBW and BIll you two have just made me so happy .. See guys we do have a sence of humor here , these guys knew I was just jokeing with them .. No need to get allout of shape everytime a post does not agree with ya .. We still have soft water for a little time more .. And thanks guys for knowing it was all in fun ... Bruce (p.S. if I have to say something to a member that is personal , PM'S ,no need to do it in public)..tight lines boys ...
Ya just have to know the person to understand them.  My uncle was one you had to know, to understand.
As one Capt said "let's make it so" and let's see what we can get into!
but was it not make it so, number one and what would you do, covered in number one
When small men begin to cast big shadows, it means that the sun is about to set.
Terry, you know what I meant...  :/ Capt, just don't have HH in the boat or you may not see your shadow due to the one he casts!
Nice new toy, Geoff!!!!  Maybe one day I'll break down and pick one up too. Hard to change my "old school" ways, lol!
